	* src/gcompris/gcompris.c: (init_background), (xrandr_init),
	(xrandr_get_config), (xrandr_set_config): fixes a crash that happens at quit time
	with xrandr set but for some reason, the xrandr variable is at NULL.
	Added signal handler on SIGSEGV to trap gcompris crash and set back the screen
	resolution.

