2005-09-27  Bruno coudoin  <bruno.coudoin@free.fr>

	Added keywords in our menu file to provide keyword searching
	for the ofset gnuedu project. It maybe usefull also for the gcompris
	website and our administratif activity filter.
	The keywords are incomplete yet.
	Fixed some warnings.


